This is fork of Steelbot 3 project (http://steelbot.ru) by vanchester (http://vanchester.ru).

Fork was created because original project died.



NEW FEATURES of fork are:

1. IRC protocol support (commands should be started with %)
2. Auto-numerical aliases for each commands
3. More than 20 new plugins
4. Each plugins sorted by categories in help info
5. Autosave timers in base and autoload when bot started



HOW TO INSTALL

run command
php /steelbot3/install/install.php create /home/steelbot/app

and answer to the questions of master.

After that go to /home/steelbot/app and run 
php run.php